Downloaded jdk-17.0.7_linux-x64_bin.tar.gz (342fb681214f4904cf26b24d7706eb2f) from
https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/javase/jdk17-archive-downloads.html and
unzipped it with 7z.  CD'ed into jdk-17.0.7, added this readme.tool file and
packed it up again using:
   7zz a -mx=9 -snl -r ../linux.amd64.jdk.v17.0.7.7z .
